summary: An Ordinance providing for the rebating and refunding of the excess portions of all assessments, not already rebated by Order of the Superior Court of the State of Washington, for King County, cause No. 63397, levied for the improvement of the alley in Block One Hundred Twenty-four (124), and One Hundred Twenty-five (125), A. A. Denny's Broadway Addition, by grading and paving the same, as provided for by Ordinance No. 14995, creating Local Improvement District No. 1347, and appropriating money for same.
